title: Can some one or riot explain how this can happen? i would love to hear !!!
body: Please take a look at the pic and tell me how this happens?

replies.body:
Unranked doesn't mean unskilled. A lot of challenger-tier players have never played ranked.

But then again getting four unranks against what is a solid team is just bad luck.

Just remember, this wasn't something like five diamonds versus two bronzies and three unranked.
